learning.unsupervised.outliers

Class LDOF

  • java.lang.Object
    • learning.unsupervised.outliers.OutlierDetector
      • learning.unsupervised.outliers.LDOF
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NSFUserInterface

    public class LDOF
extends OutlierDetector
implements NSFUserInterface
    This class implements the local distance-based outlier factor that was proposed in the paper titled 'A New Local Distance-Based Outlier Detection Approach for Scattered Real-World Data' by Ke Zhang and Marcus Hutter and Huidong Jin at PAKDD 2009. The LDOF factor is the ratio between the average distance to the k-NNs and the average distance among the k-NNs.
